1: how to creat a hidden file or folder with CLI?
to creat a hidden folder I will use mkdir .hiddenfolder
to creat a hidden file I will use touch .hiddenfile
to display the hidden file or folder i will use li -a

2:how do I creat multiple nested directories ?
i will use the command mkdir -p c/users/myusername/these/folders/are/just/for/fun

3:how do I append a message to a file ?
I will use (echo "first message" ; echo "secound message") >> CLI-challenge

